# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-06-02 11:43

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:13
translate portuguese lisa11_923fd11f:

    # "I lie in bed and slowly drift off to sleep."
    "Deito-me na cama e adormeço lentamente."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:14
translate portuguese lisa11_13cbfc43:

    # "Then I hear the door to my bedroom open."
    "Depois ouço a porta do meu quarto a abrir-se."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:18
translate portuguese lisa11_9c5bdb22:

    # sp "Honey?"
    sp "Querido?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:19
translate portuguese lisa11_08868f48:

    # "Lisa stands over me, looking at me nervously."
    "A Lisa está em pé ao meu lado, a olhar para mim nervosamente."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:20
translate portuguese lisa11_9daec7e2:

    # pc "Hey, [mom]. Are you here to patch things up? I really want things to go back to the way they were."
    pc "Olá, [mom]. Estás aqui para fazer as pazes? Quero mesmo que as coisas voltem a ser como eram."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:23
translate portuguese lisa11_b6018e7a:

    # "She sits on the bed and looks away, her eyes filled with sadness."
    "Ela senta-se na cama e desvia o olhar, com os olhos cheios de tristeza."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:24
translate portuguese lisa11_faf75111:

    # sp "No... um... I'm not ready to talk about that yet."
    sp "Não... hum... ainda não estou pronto para falar sobre isso."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:25
translate portuguese lisa11_d690a0fb:

    # sp "That's not why I'm here."
    sp "Não é por isso que estou aqui."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:28
translate portuguese lisa11_698f3156:

    # "She holds out her hand and opens it, revealing a small key."
    "Ela estende a mão e abre-a, revelando uma pequena chave."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:29
translate portuguese lisa11_f971e6b8:

    # sp "I was changing the sheets on my bed, and I pulled the bed out from the wall a little."
    sp "Estava a mudar os lençóis da minha cama e afastei-a um pouco da parede."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:30
translate portuguese lisa11_14a984c4:

    # sp "This key was between the bed and the wall, like it had fallen there and gotten stuck."
    sp "Esta chave estava entre a cama e a parede, como se tivesse caído ali e ficado presa."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:31
translate portuguese lisa11_07383f08:

    # sp "I have no idea what it might go to. It must have been your father's though."
    sp "Não faço ideia do que possa abrir. Mas deve ter sido do teu pai."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:32
translate portuguese lisa11_29cefead:

    # sp "You've been looking into his things some, right? Do you have any idea what it might unlock?"
    sp "Tens andado a vasculhar as coisas dele, certo? Tens alguma ideia do que possa abrir?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:33
translate portuguese lisa11_cb4f15ad:

    # pc "I'm not sure."
    pc "Não tenho a certeza."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:36
translate portuguese lisa11_bcb67439:

    # sp "Well why don't you take it. You've been looking into his disappearance more than I have, I know. Maybe you can find what it goes to."
    sp "Bem, porque não a levas? Tens andado a investigar o desaparecimento dele mais do que eu, eu sei. Talvez consigas descobrir o que ela abre."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:37
translate portuguese lisa11_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Está bem."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:38
translate portuguese lisa11_992dd270:

    # sp "Just let me know if you find anything. Okay, honey?"
    sp "Avisas-me se descobrires alguma coisa. Está bem, querida?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:39
translate portuguese lisa11_01171d90:

    # pc "Okay, [mom]."
    pc "Está bem, [mom]."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:40
translate portuguese lisa11_e80f0a5a:

    # sp "And we'll deal with the other... stuff... some other time."
    sp "E tratamos das outras... coisas... noutra altura."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:41
translate portuguese lisa11_dfa9ae3b:

    # sp "I just need a little more time to think about all of this."
    sp "Só preciso de um pouco mais de tempo para pensar em tudo isto."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:44
translate portuguese lisa11_981522fd:

    # "With that, she stands up and starts to walk out of the room."
    "Dito isto, ela levanta-se e começa a sair do quarto."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:46
translate portuguese lisa11_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_goodnight.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_goodnight.wav'

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:47
translate portuguese lisa11_504e6893:

    # sp "Good night, honey. I love you."
    sp "Boa noite, querida. Amo-te."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:48
translate portuguese lisa11_93df423a:

    # pc "Love you too, [mom]."
    pc "Também te amo, [mom]."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:51
translate portuguese lisa11_1ce407a4:

    # "She walks out and shuts the door."
    "Ela sai e fecha a porta."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:52
translate portuguese lisa11_17bdeaa1:

    # "I put the key on the night stand, thinking of places that it might go to."
    "Coloquei a chave na mesinha de cabeceira, a pensar nos sítios onde ela poderia servir."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:53
translate portuguese lisa11_6eb1c739:

    # "I'll be sure to look around tomorrow."
    "Vou dar uma vista de olhos amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:72
translate portuguese lisa11b_45041214:

    # "I walk down into the basement to look around. Maybe there's something down here that the key goes to?"
    "Desço até à cave para dar uma vista de olhos. Talvez haja aqui em baixo algo a que a chave sirva?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:75
translate portuguese lisa11b_0ce52b58:

    # "I'm not really sure where to start though. Was there anything down here that was locked?"
    "Mas não sei bem por onde começar. Havia alguma coisa aqui em baixo que estivesse trancada?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:78
translate portuguese lisa11b_24c55b3a:

    # "Oh wait a minute. The safe. Could this key go to that?"
    "Espera lá um minuto. O cofre. Será que esta chave serve para isso?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:81
translate portuguese lisa11b_7d9788e7:

    # "I walk over and kneel down in front of the safe. It has a dial on the front, but that seems like it's just for show."
    "Aproximo-me e ajoelho-me em frente ao cofre. Tem um mostrador na frente, mas parece que é só para enfeite."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:82
translate portuguese lisa11b_1e8bf5d6:

    # "There is a keyhole directly in the center of the dial, and the key Lisa gave me fits into it perfectly."
    "Há uma fechadura mesmo no centro do mostrador, e a chave que a Lisa me deu encaixa na perfeição."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:83
translate portuguese lisa11b_968ff7d2:

    # "I turn the key, then pull the handle and open the safe."
    "Giro a chave, puxo a alavanca e abro o cofre."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:86
translate portuguese lisa11b_cd2be96e:

    # pc "Woah."
    pc "Uau."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:87
translate portuguese lisa11b_f4993b24:

    # "I have no idea how much money that is, but it's a lot."
    "Não faço ideia de quanto dinheiro é isto, mas é muito."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:88
translate portuguese lisa11b_2b8392cf:

    # "And in front of all of the cash is an envelope that has Lisa's name on it."
    "E à frente de todo o dinheiro está um envelope com o nome da Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:89
translate portuguese lisa11b_f4df4ca9:

    # "Dad must have left all of this for her."
    "O pai deve ter deixado tudo isto para ela."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:92
translate portuguese lisa11b_0652396e:

    # "I pick up the envelope. I half-consider opening it and taking a look myself."
    "Pego no envelope. Quase que penso em abri-lo e dar uma espreitadela."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:93
translate portuguese lisa11b_2a644210:

    # "I shouldn't though. Better to give it to her. It's probably personal."
    "Mas não devo. É melhor dar-lho a ela. Provavelmente é pessoal."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:94
translate portuguese lisa11b_86e4569e:

    # "At least she won't have to worry about bills for a while."
    "Pelo menos ela não vai ter de se preocupar com contas por um tempo."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:97
translate portuguese lisa11b_a6707303:

    # "I close the safe and take the key and the letter with me, then leave the basement."
    "Fecho o cofre e levo a chave e a carta comigo, depois saio da cave."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:104
translate portuguese lisa11b_74736304:

    # "I should get to school."
    "Tenho de ir para a escola."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:120
translate portuguese lisa11c_3227967b:

    # "I go to Lisa's room and push the door open slightly. She's lying on her bed, looking away from me."
    "Vou até ao quarto da Lisa e empurro a porta ligeiramente. Ela está deitada na cama, a desviar o olhar de mim."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:121
translate portuguese lisa11c_18e46dc8:

    # pc "Hey [mom], are you sleeping?"
    pc "Olá [mom], estás a dormir?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:122
translate portuguese lisa11c_cd4f18c7:

    # sp "No, not sleeping. Just resting."
    sp "Não, não estou a dormir. Só a descansar."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:123
translate portuguese lisa11c_3dff98b0:

    # "I'm surprised, she doesn't even turn towards me."
    "Fico surpreendido, ela nem sequer se vira para mim."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:124
translate portuguese lisa11c_76e7237c:

    # sp "Did you need something?"
    sp "Precisavas de alguma coisa?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:125
translate portuguese lisa11c_7b8e5b75:

    # pc "I found what the key went to. It opened a safe in the basement."
    pc "Descobri para onde era a chave. Abriu um cofre na cave."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:126
translate portuguese lisa11c_7bd6a230:

    # sp "Oh really? What was in it?"
    sp "A sério? O que é que tinha lá dentro?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:127
translate portuguese lisa11c_5f5da353:

    # pc "Enough money that you're not going to have to worry about things for a while."
    pc "Dinheiro suficiente para que não tenhas de te preocupar com nada por algum tempo."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:130
translate portuguese lisa11c_9cc3ee2f:

    # sp "What? Really?"
    sp "O quê? A sério?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:131
translate portuguese lisa11c_db707b75:

    # pc "Yeah, there has to be several thousand dollars in there, at least."
    pc "Sim, deve haver lá vários milhares de dólares, pelo menos."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:132
translate portuguese lisa11c_8430e1a8:

    # pc "And there was this envelope. It's for you."
    pc "E havia um envelope. É para ti."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:135
translate portuguese lisa11c_5651902f:

    # sp "For me?"
    sp "Para mim?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:136
translate portuguese lisa11c_40f0697c:

    # sp "Your dad left me a note and a bunch of money?"
    sp "O teu pai deixou-me um bilhete e um monte de dinheiro?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:137
translate portuguese lisa11c_c02b520f:

    # pc "It seems that way."
    pc "Parece que sim."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:138
translate portuguese lisa11c_fd67cf4b:

    # sp "Did you open it?"
    sp "Abriste-o?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:139
translate portuguese lisa11c_6b7c31f4:

    # pc "No, it was meant for you, not me."
    pc "Não, era para ti, não para mim."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:142
translate portuguese lisa11c_82c596b9:

    # "She opens up the envelope and pulls out a long, hand-written letter. I recognize my father's almost illegible scrawl immediately."
    "Ela abre o envelope e tira uma longa carta escrita à mão. Reconheço imediatamente a caligrafia quase ilegível do meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:143
translate portuguese lisa11c_8b4394a6:

    # sp "\"Dear Lisa, I'm sorry to leave without telling you anything. I'm afraid you'll try to stop me and I think you would succeed.\""
    sp "«Querida Lisa, desculpa ir-me embora sem te dizer nada. Tenho medo que tentes impedir-me e acho que conseguirias.»"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:144
translate portuguese lisa11c_515254e5:

    # sp "\"Or that you would think that I am out of my mind, and lock me in some institution. Maybe that is where I should be.\""
    sp "«Ou que pensasses que estou louco e me trancasses numa instituição. Talvez seja lá que eu deva estar.»"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:145
translate portuguese lisa11c_74cb1071:

    # sp "\"I have built a machine. I am going to use it to find her...\""
    sp "«Construí uma máquina. Vou usá-la para a encontrar...»"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:148
translate portuguese lisa11c_11f5d677:

    # "Lisa continues reading the note, though her voice trails away as tears begin flowing down her cheeks."
    "A Lisa continua a ler o bilhete, embora a sua voz se vá esmorando à medida que as lágrimas começam a escorrer-lhe pelas bochechas."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:149
translate portuguese lisa11c_8f38bc28:

    # "I put my arm around her, trying to comfort her, not really knowing what to do."
    "Passo o braço à volta dela, tentando consolá-la, sem saber bem o que fazer."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:152
translate portuguese lisa11c_121db800:

    # "When she finishes reading the letter, she crumples it into a ball and throws it across the room, scowling."
    "Quando termina de ler a carta, amassa-a e atira-a para o outro lado da sala, com um ar carrancudo."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:154
translate portuguese lisa11c_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_fuckingbastard.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_fuckingbastard.wav'

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:155
translate portuguese lisa11c_a5382b91:

    # sp "FUCK! Fucking bastard! I can't believe him!"
    sp "FODA-SE! Seu cabrão de merda! Não acredito nele!"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:158
translate portuguese lisa11c_2aaac290:

    # "She turns and collapses into my arms, squeezing me tight."
    "Ela vira-se e desaba nos meus braços, apertando-me com força."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:160
translate portuguese lisa11c_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_bastard.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_bastard.wav'

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:161
translate portuguese lisa11c_dd0de08b:

    # sp "Bastard..."
    sp "Cabrão..."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:162
translate portuguese lisa11c_3865529e:

    # "I just hold her as she sobs into my chest, her tears soaking through my shirt."
    "Limito-me a abraçá-la enquanto ela soluçava contra o meu peito, as lágrimas a encharcarem-me a camisa."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:163
translate portuguese lisa11c_4ed1e745:

    # "She keeps crying for I don't know how long. Until no more tears are coming out, and her breathing begins to slow down."
    "Ela continua a chorar durante não sei quanto tempo. Até que as lágrimas deixam de cair e a respiração dela começa a abrandar."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:167
translate portuguese lisa11c_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_sorry3.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_sorry3.wav'

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:168
translate portuguese lisa11c_89be2b54:

    # sp "I'm sorry."
    sp "Desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:169
translate portuguese lisa11c_f713d4de:

    # pc "It's okay. Whatever you need, [mom]. I'm here for you."
    pc "Não faz mal. O que precisares, [mom]. Estou aqui para ti."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:170
translate portuguese lisa11c_8c19424d:

    # sp "Will you stay with me tonight? Just sleep with me. Hold me. Nothing more."
    sp "Ficas comigo esta noite? Dorme comigo. Abraça-me. Nada mais."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:171
translate portuguese lisa11c_bc12ce42:

    # sp "I just don't want to be alone."
    sp "Só não quero ficar sozinha."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:172
translate portuguese lisa11c_23aaba02:

    # pc "Sure [mom]. Of course."
    pc "Claro, [mom]. Claro que sim."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:175
translate portuguese lisa11c_12454e17:

    # "I lie with her, holding her."
    "Deito-me ao lado dela, abraçando-a."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:176
translate portuguese lisa11c_0d3176d3:

    # "When I try to ask her what was in the letter, she starts crying again."
    "Quando tento perguntar-lhe o que estava na carta, ela começa a chorar outra vez."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:177
translate portuguese lisa11c_60ee0c75:

    # "Then she falls asleep. Her sobs finally stopping. After a while, I fall asleep too."
    "Depois adormece. Os seus soluços finalmente param. Passado algum tempo, adormeço também."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:180
translate portuguese lisa11c_1f57e518:

    # "I sleep harder than I expected to. It must be from all the drama. All the worrying about Dad."
    "Durmo mais profundamente do que esperava. Deve ser por causa de todo o drama. De toda a preocupação com o pai."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:181
translate portuguese lisa11c_fbbfecd8:

    # "And worrying about Lisa too."
    "E com a Lisa também."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:184
translate portuguese lisa11c_897fedc8:

    # "I must have slept through her getting up in the night, because when I wake up in the morning, she's gone and there's another note on the bed."
    "Devo ter dormido enquanto ela se levantava durante a noite, porque quando acordo de manhã, ela já se foi e há outro bilhete na cama."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:187
translate portuguese lisa11c_dbbfa079:

    # "I anxiously pick it up and read it."
    "Pego nele ansiosamente e leio-o."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:188
translate portuguese lisa11c_46f47007:

    # "\"Thank you for last night. You were exactly what I needed right now. I still need time to think about things though.\""
    "«Obrigada pela noite passada. Foste exatamente o que eu precisava neste momento. Mas ainda preciso de tempo para pensar nas coisas.»"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:189
translate portuguese lisa11c_b7a30203:

    # "\"But I love you. Very much.\""
    "«Mas amo-te. Muito.»"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:190
translate portuguese lisa11c_f2b9cd11:

    # "\"-Lisa\""
    "\"-Lisa\""

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:193
translate portuguese lisa11c_22b22b07:

    # "Hopefully this is one step closer to making things okay between us again."
    "Espero que isto seja mais um passo para que as coisas voltem a ficar bem entre nós."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:3
    old "Wait a few days after the previous scene."
    new "Espera alguns dias após a cena anterior."

    # game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa11.rpy:4
    old "Then this scene will happen automatically when you sleep at home."
    new "Depois, esta cena acontecerá automaticamente quando dormires em casa."

